snippet.title: Enotria: The Last Song - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer  | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Enotria: The Last Song is a single-player soulslike RPG developed by Jyamma Games. Don role-altering masks, engage in tough combat encounters, and unravel the secrets of Enotria inspired by Italian folklore. Enotria: The Last Song is launching on September 19 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam and Epic Games Store) with a demo available now on PlayStation 5 (PS5) and Steam.

#Gaming #GameTrailers #Games
